11. Remove Duplicate Customer IDs : 
-----------------------------------------------------
Problem
int[] arr = {1,2,2,3,4,4,5};

for(int i=0;i<arr.length;i++)
{
    boolean duplicate = false;

    for(int j=0;j<i;j++)
    {
        if(arr[i]==arr[j])
        {
            duplicate=true;
            break;
        }
    }

    if(!duplicate)
        System.out.print(arr[i]+" ");
}


